<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA624_01_IH_0002</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema624_01.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_01_ih_0002">
      <section class="title flex_wrap">
        <h2 lang="y">
          <span class="recap" lang="y">이전에 <span>배웠어요</span></span>
          <span class="title_text" lang="y">『수학 6-1』 비와 비율 알아보기</span>
        </h2>
      </section>
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2_deep_green" lang="y">비에서 기준량과 비교하는 양을 찾아 쓰고, 비율을 분수와 소수로 각각 나타내어 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center align_start">
          <div class="table_wrap">
            <table>
              <colgroup>
                <col />
                <col />
                <col />
                <col />
                <col />
              </colgroup>
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col" rowspan="2" lang="y">비</th>
                  <th scope="col" rowspan="2" lang="y">기준량</th>
                  <th scope="col" rowspan="2" lang="y">비교하는 양</th>
                  <th scope="col" colspan="2" lang="y">비율</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col" lang="y">분수</th>
                  <th scope="col" lang="y">소수</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="row" lang="y">3:4</th>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="(3)/(4)" class="w_80"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="0.75"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="row" lang="y">20에 대한 11의 비</th>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="20"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="11"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="(11)/(20)" class="w_80"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="0.55"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
					<div class="inner_solve">
						<div class="flex">
							<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
							<div class="conts_solve">
								<p>
									3 : 4에서 기준량은 4, 비교하는 양은 3이고, 비율을 분수로 나타내면
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>3</span>
                    <span>4</span>
                  </span>, 소수로 나타내면 <br/>0.75입니다.
                  20에 대한 11의 비는 11 : 20이므로 기준량은 20, 비교하는 양은 11이고,
                </p>
                <p class="mt_15">
                  비율을 분수로 나타내면
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>11</span>
                    <span>20</span>
                  </span>, 소수로 나타내면 0.55입니다.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
